{"tid":941260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一生中最愛","createTime":"2018-12-14T15:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T16:49:55.000Z","uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05e8e37a5172137525e1bb5bdaa04ca18a139516","tid":941260,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"如果痴痴的等某日 終於可等到一生中最愛<br />\n誰介意你我這段情 每每碰上了意外不清楚未來<br />\n何曾願意 我心中所愛 每天要孤單看海<br />\n<br />\n寧願一生都不說話 都不想講假說話欺騙你<br />\n留意到你我這段情 你會發覺間隔著一點點距離<br />\n無言地愛 我偏不敢說 說一句想跟你一起 喔喔<br />\n<br />\n如真 如假 如可分身飾演自己<br />\n會將心中的溫柔 獻出給你唯有的知己<br />\n如痴 如醉 還盼你懂珍惜自己<br />\n有天即使分離我都想你 我 真的想你"},{"pid":"b9f1fd8c37b74737ec901800581c73e04afe6612","tid":941260,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:38:42.000Z","msg":"努力努力"},{"pid":"f731423226e8890b3fb9848ae23fead7c931667b","tid":941260,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"290b96432439c9bbfad6c9f78fa02585d4252b6f","tid":941260,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fFzlU_DbW3U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfFzlU_DbW3U&d=M1cunQxZFzHJAHuAEZ8SVr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a1d210e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fFzlU_DbW3U</a>"},{"pid":"3670874d9e898a4566d6f3cba0cadf11517e25b1","tid":941260,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"290b96432439c9bbfad6c9f78fa02585d4252b6f","tid":941260,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fFzlU_DbW3U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfFzlU_DbW3U&d=M1cunQxZFzHJAHuAEZ8SVr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a1d210e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/w